{"tid":1518544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方指明天以不同理由上街遊行可能違法","createTime":"2019-08-30T09:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:11:58.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"88fb21cdcb2a25bf339b1c830c8a0f74fa0d9243","tid":1518544,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方表示留意到有人計劃明天以不同理由上街遊行，例如去銅鑼灣行街、到維園賞花、831自由行，以及宗教遊行等，指這些行為可能涉嫌非法集結，警方會適時採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n警方又說過去一天，針對過去兩個月來的違法活動再拘捕了七人，分別涉及六月廿一日包圍警察總部、七月一日闖入立法會、七月十三日上水遊行、七月十四日沙田遊行，以及721元朗襲擊事件，重申任何案件不理當事人背景，都會嚴厲跟進。"},{"pid":"e2bfd0cf4d8360dd1428c46597bd1c8e348a45a3","tid":1518544,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"兩句講哂<br />\n831無大台 出中環<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=784d01f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=114d5454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: s